name: Foss project
body:
This is a starter project for our FOSS class in college under our undergraduate course in computer science.  
Our IRC channel is #foss_class on [freenode](https://webchat.freeenode.net).  
You can join our mailing list foss_class@googlegroups.com  
For further details contact  
[Nareesh Devaraj](https://github.com/nareesh/foss_project/)  
[Sai Hemanth](https://github.com/)

Our project mentor is [Mr. Dayanand V](https://github.com/dayanandv)
